  <div class="pt-section pt-section1 section1 pt-flex pt-flex-center pt-flex-column bg-black">
    <div class="pt-section-content pt-text-center pt-margin-bottom-large">
      <h3 class="pt-section-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">MAGNETIC FUNCTIONALITY</h3>
      <p class="pt-section-detail text-base text-gray-400 mb-8 sm:mb-12 ">
        With built-in metal strips, the MagEZ Case Pro attaches easily to the
        MagEZ Series magnetic wireless chargers for an uninterrupted charging
        experience.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-section-picture">
      <picture>
        <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}"
          data-src="{{   'product-casepro-section1-iphone11.png' | asset_url }}"
          class="img-responsive lazyload" />
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="pt-section section2 pt-flex pt-flex-center pt-bg-dark bg-black">
    <div class="pt-section-content">
      <h3 class="pt-section-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">5 PROTECTIVE LAYERS</h3>
      <p class="pt-section-detail text-base text-gray-400 mb-8 sm:mb-12 ">
        Scientifically designed using layers of premium materials, including three
        layers of aramid fiber, a shock-absorbing EVA foam layer, and a microfiber
        lining to cushion your phone.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-section-picture">
      <picture>
        <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}"
          data-src="{{   'product-casepro-section2-iphone11.png' | asset_url }}"
          class="img-responsive lazyload" />
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="pt-section section3 pt-flex pt-flex-center bg-black">
    <div class="pt-section-picture">
      <picture>
        <img src="{{ placeholder_gif }}"
        data-src="{{ 'product-casepro-section3.png' | asset_url }}" class="img-responsive width-100 lazyload" />
      </picture>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-section-content">
      <h3 class="pt-section-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
        MILITARY DROP TESTED
      </h3>
      <p class="pt-section-detail text-base text-gray-400 mb-8 sm:mb-12 pt-margin-bottom-medium">
        With a TPU (Thermoplastic Polyurethane) reinforced frame, corner bumpers,
        and shock-absorbing air pockets, the MagEZ Case Pro can receive an impact
        without damaging your phone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="pt-section section4 pt-flex pt-flex-center bg-black">
    <div class="pt-section-content">
      <h3 class="pt-section-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
        ANTI-SLIP SIDE GRIPS
      </h3>
      <p class="pt-section-detail text-base text-gray-400 mb-8 sm:mb-12 ">
        Additional textured side grips ensure a firmer hold, reducing the chances
